8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Airtable AI and Amie share a solid foundation of core features including Task Management, Ai Assistant, Calendar, Collaboration. Where Airtable AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Automation and Templates and Analytics, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Airtable AI holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Amie scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Airtable AI and Amie offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Airtable AI's free tier and Amie's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
